 os-prober,
 rsync,
 fll-live-initscripts
Suggests: gparted,
 distro-defaults
Description: backend scripts to install siduction to hdd
 fll-installer provides a framework for installing siduction Live Linux
 to hard disk drives.
 .
 This is a FULLSTORY live-only package and should not be installed to an
 ordinary system.
